obj_root_law_sections_1:
  sectionId (20871)
  sectionNo (1)
  orderNo 1
  title `Short title and commencement.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_1_content
  footnotes `1. 12th April, 2016, vide notification No. S.O. 1384 (E), dated 11th April, 2016, see Gazette of India, Part II, sec. 3(ii).`
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_7_7_00016_201617_1517807328429&sectionId=20871&sectionno=1&orderno=1&orgactid=AC_CEN_7_7_00016_201617_1517807328429
obj_root_law_sections_1_content:
  string
  line `(1) This Act may be called the National Waterways Act, 2016.`
  line
  line `(2) It shall come into force on such date ^1`
  line `as the Central Government may, by notification in the`
  line `Official Gazette, appoint.`
obj_root_law_sections_2:
  sectionId (20872)
  sectionNo (2)
  orderNo 2
  title `Existing national waterways and declaration of certain inland waterways as national waterways.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_2_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_2_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_7_7_00016_201617_1517807328429&sectionId=20872&sectionno=2&orderno=2&orgactid=AC_CEN_7_7_00016_201617_1517807328429
obj_root_law_sections_2_content:
  string
  line `(1) The existing national waterways specified at serial numbers 1 to 5 in the Schedule along`
  line `with their limits given in column (3) thereof, which have been declared as such under the Acts referred to`
  line `in sub-section (1) of section 5, shall, subject to the modifications made under this Act, continue to be`
  line `national waterways for the purposes of shipping and navigation under this Act.`
  line
  line `(2) The regulation and development of the waterways referred to in sub-section (1) which have been`
  line `under the control of the Central Government shall continue, as if the said waterways are declared as`
  line `national waterways under the provisions of this Act.`
  line
  line `(3) The inland waterways specified at serial numbers 6 to 111 in the Schedule along with their limits`
  line `given in column (3) thereof are hereby declared to be national waterways for the purposes of shipping and`
  line navigation.
obj_root_law_sections_2_footnotes:
  string
  line
obj_root_law_sections_3:
  sectionId (20873)
  sectionNo (3)
  orderNo 3
  title `Declaration as to expediency of control and development by Union of waterways specified in Schedule for certain purposes.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_3_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_3_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_7_7_00016_201617_1517807328429&sectionId=20873&sectionno=3&orderno=3&orgactid=AC_CEN_7_7_00016_201617_1517807328429
obj_root_law_sections_3_content:
  string
  line `Save as provided in sub-sections (1) and (2) of section 2, it is hereby`
  line `declared that it is expedient in the public interest that the Union should take under its control the`
  line `regulation and development of the waterways specified in the Schedule for the purposes of shipping and`
  line `navigation to the extent provided in the Inland Waterways Authority of India Act, 1985 (82 of 1985).`
obj_root_law_sections_3_footnotes:
  string
  line
obj_root_law_sections_4:
  sectionId (20874)
  sectionNo (4)
  orderNo 4
  title `Amendment of section 2 of Act 82 of 1985.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_4_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_4_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_7_7_00016_201617_1517807328429&sectionId=20874&sectionno=4&orderno=4&orgactid=AC_CEN_7_7_00016_201617_1517807328429
obj_root_law_sections_4_content:
  string
  line `In the Inland Waterways Authority of India`
  line `Act, 1985, in section 2, for clause (h), the following clause shall be substituted, namely:—`
  line
  line `'(h) "national waterway" means the inland waterway declared by section 2 of the National`
  line `Waterways Act, 2016, to be a national waterway.`
  line
  line `Explanation.—If Parliament declares by law any other waterway to be a national waterway, then,`
  line `from the date on which such declaration takes effect, such other waterway—`
  line
  line `(i) shall also be deemed to be a national waterway within the meaning of this clause; and`
  line
  line `(ii) the provisions of this Act shall, with necessary modifications (including modification for`
  line `construing any reference to the commencement of this Act as a reference to the date aforesaid),`
  line `apply to such national waterway;'.`
obj_root_law_sections_4_footnotes:
  string
  line
obj_root_law_sections_5:
  sectionId (20875)
  sectionNo (5)
  orderNo 5
  title `Repeal of certain enactments and saving.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_5_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_5_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_7_7_00016_201617_1517807328429&sectionId=20875&sectionno=5&orderno=5&orgactid=AC_CEN_7_7_00016_201617_1517807328429
obj_root_law_sections_5_content:
  string
  line `(1) The following Acts, namely:—`
  line
  line `(a) the National Waterway (Allahabad-Haldia Stretch of the Ganga Bhagirathi-Hooghly River)`
  line `Act, 1982 (49 of 1982);`
  line
  line `(b) the National Waterway (Sadiya-Dhubri Stretch of Brahmaputra River) Act, 1988`
  line `(40 of 1988);`
  line
  line `(c) the National Waterway (Kollam-Kottapuram Stretch of West Coast Canal and Champakara`
  line `and Udyogmandal Canals) Act, 1992 (25 of 1992);`
  line
  line `(d) the National Waterway (Talcher-Dhamra Stretch of Rivers, Geonkhali-Charbatia Stretch of`
  line `East Coast Canal, Charbatia-Dhamra Stretch of Matai River and Mahanadi Delta Rivers) Act, 2008`
  line `(23 of 2008); and`
  line
  line `(e) the National Waterway (Kakinada-Puducherry Stretch of Canals and the Kaluvelly Tank,`
  line `Bhadrachalam-Rajahmundry Stretch of River Godavari and Wazirabad-Vijayawada Stretch of River`
  line `Krishna) Act, 2008 (24 of 2008),`
  line
  line `are hereby repealed.`
  line
  line `(2) Notwithstanding such repeal, anything done or any action taken under the Acts referred to in`
  line `sub-section (1), in so far as they are in conformity with the provisions of this Act, shall be deemed to have`
  line `been done or omitted to be done or taken or not taken under the provisions of this Act.`
obj_root_law_sections_5_footnotes:
  string
  line
